OL,3,CHundreds of jobs saved as deal agreed
OL,4,Cto buy Brace's Bakery in Newport
OL,6,FHundreds of jobs have been saved at
OL,7,FBrace's Bakery after a buyer was found
OL,8,Fto keep the company open.
OL,10,FThe survival of the almost 125 year
OL,11,Fold bakery was in doubt following
OL,12,Frecent financial pressures at the
OL,13,Fcompany.
OL,15,FHowever, on Friday June 5, Boparan
OL,16,FPrivate Office announced they have
OL,17,Facquired the Newport based bakery
OL,18,Fsecuring around 250 jobs.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
