OL,3,CHundreds of jobs saved as deal agreed
OL,4,Cto buy Brace's Bakery in Newport
OL,6,FIn a statement released on 5 June
OL,7,FRanjit Singh Boparan, President of
OL,8,FBoparan Private Office, said: "Brace's
OL,9,Fis an iconic brand with a rich
OL,10,Fheritage, and we are delighted to have
OL,11,Fbeen able to reach an agreement to
OL,12,Fstep in and preserve this business,
OL,13,Fwhile helping to take it into a new
OL,14,Fera through investment, innovation and
OL,15,Fmodernisation.
OL,17,F"Brace's Bakery has been at the heart
OL,18,Fof its communities for generations,
OL,19,Fand we are absolutely committed to
OL,20,Fsupporting its long-term success.
OL,26,@pD@_OUyD@AOU
