OL,3,CHundreds of jobs saved as deal agreed
OL,4,Cto buy Brace's Bakery in Newport
OL,6,F"Our focus is on providing the backing
OL,7,Fand stability the business needs to
OL,8,Fmove forward and build a sustainable
OL,9,Ffuture while maintaining the identity
OL,10,Fand quality that customers trust."
OL,12,FEstablished in 1902, Brace's Bakery is
OL,13,Fa fourth-generation family business
OL,14,Fbased in Newport.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
