OL,3,CHundreds of jobs saved as deal agreed
OL,4,Cto buy Brace's Bakery in Newport
OL,6,FMark Brace, Managing Director at
OL,7,FBrace's Bakery, said: "This is an
OL,8,Fimportant step for Brace's Bakery, and
OL,9,Fmy brother and fellow director,
OL,10,FJonathan, and I are both delighted
OL,11,Fthat Boparan Private Office has
OL,12,Fstepped in to give the brand the
OL,13,Fopportunity to build on almost 125
OL,14,Fyears of baking heritage as we move
OL,15,Finto a new era.
