OL,3,CHundreds of jobs saved as deal agreed
OL,4,Cto buy Brace's Bakery in Newport
OL,6,F"Boparan Private Office understands
OL,7,Fthe importance of the Brace's brand,
OL,8,Fits people and the communities we
OL,9,Fserve. Their support provides a clear
OL,10,Fpath forward for the business,
OL,11,Fallowing us to focus on strengthening
OL,12,FBrace's operations and continuing to
OL,13,Fdeliver the quality products our
OL,14,Fcustomers expect."
